
UPDATE competencies SET description='Solid understanding of the site HSE Case, including Major Accident Hazards and Bowties, MOPO and SIMOPS requirements, Emergency Response Procedures, and communication protocols. Application of this knowledge to maintain safe operations, recognise and manage risk, ensure compliance with operating limits, and respond effectively to abnormal and emergency situations.'
WHERE id='22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222201';

UPDATE competencies SET description='Comprehensive and detailed understanding of the plant and process, including the ability to interpret and apply key technical documents such as P&IDs, Process Control Narratives and control loops, Cause & Effects, Process Safeguarding Memorandum, and HAZOP studies. Used to ensure safe, stable, and efficient operation, effective troubleshooting, and informed decision-making under both normal and abnormal conditions.'
WHERE id='22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222202';

UPDATE competencies SET description='Sound operational understanding of key plant equipment, such as compressors and packaged units. Covers basic operating principles, performance characteristics, normal operating ranges, and common failure modes — supporting safe operation, effective monitoring, early fault detection, and appropriate response to equipment-related issues.'
WHERE id='22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222203';

UPDATE competencies SET description='Thorough understanding and correct application of all applicable Standard Operating Procedures (SOPs), including Initial Start-Up Procedures (ISUP), Normal Operating Procedures, and other relevant operational guidelines — enabling accurate execution to ensure safe, efficient, and compliant plant operation under both normal and abnormal conditions.'
WHERE id='22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222204';

UPDATE competencies SET description='Fundamental competencies required to manage the significant operational risks associated with production activities. Covers Management of Change (MOC), safe shift handovers, process safety hazard control, and fire and explosion protection — including the mandate to Stabilise, Slowdown, or Shutdown an installation to ensure the safety of staff and the facility when a deviation occurs.'
WHERE id='22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222205';

UPDATE competencies SET description='Proficiency in understanding and using Human-Machine Interface (HMI) tools and technical functionalities within the Distributed Control System (DCS) / Integrated Control and Safeguarding System. Covers effective navigation, monitoring, alarm management, trend analysis, and utilisation of control and safeguarding features to ensure safe, reliable, and efficient plant operation.'
WHERE id='22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222210';

UPDATE competencies SET description='Understanding the significance of process variable limits and effective use of the Master Alarm Database to anticipate, monitor, and prevent potential operational issues.'
WHERE id='22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222211';

UPDATE competencies SET description='Proactive identification of potential threats and opportunities through effective application of approved Monitoring Plans — enabling early intervention to address process or equipment performance issues and optimise operations. For Field Operators, this includes proactive monitoring rounds in the assigned area, recording key process parameters at agreed frequency, reporting operational exceedances, and identifying abnormal conditions (e.g., minor leaks, unusual noise, vibration) early with timely corrective action or escalation.'
WHERE id='22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222212';

UPDATE competencies SET description='Effective shift handovers through clear, structured communication that ensures full situational awareness of process conditions, risks, mitigation measures, equipment status, and ongoing operational or maintenance activities. Covers the four key elements: Shift Handover (SH) / Crew Change, Start of Shift Orientation (SoSO), Shift Team Meeting (STM), and End of Shift Report (EoSR) — ensuring the incoming shift understands threats to the production plan, mitigations, and equipment availability to meet the plan safely.'
WHERE id='22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222213';

UPDATE competencies SET description='Recognition of and response to abnormal situations using a structured approach to safely restore normal operations. Includes application of Stabilise, Slowdown, or Shutdown (SSS) principles to protect personnel and assets, effective use of available references (alarm databases, procedures, manuals), and timely escalation to the team and Operations staff when required.'
WHERE id='22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222214';

UPDATE competencies SET description='Strict adherence to the requirements for bypassing safety controls — including formal authorisation before overriding or disabling safety-critical equipment via MOS. Covers full understanding of the consequences and process safety risks of applying MOS, proper recording and maintenance of all MOS applications, and accurate use of the operational register and End of Shift Report (EoSR) to log triggers, actions taken, and mitigations for every abnormal situation.'
WHERE id='22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222215';

UPDATE competencies SET description='Approval and verification of isolations (LOTO / energy isolation), safe handover of systems for maintenance, and confirmation of reinstatement after work completion.'
WHERE id='22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222220';

UPDATE competencies SET description='Performance of CLAIR (Cleaning, Lubrication, Adjustment, Inspect and Repair) on assigned critical equipment in the assigned area as described in Maintenance Assist, first-line troubleshooting within defined limits, and support to maintenance activities while safeguarding equipment integrity and process safety.'
WHERE id='22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222';

UPDATE competencies SET description='Verification of PTW and assurance that all activities within the area of custody comply with HSE and Permit requirements; confirmation that work is safe to proceed including gas testing; support to Maintenance, Contractors and vendors performing concurrent operations as Area Authority; management of SIMOPS; verification of isolations, barriers and safeguards; control of hazards; and maintenance of Operational Registers within the Area of Custody.'
WHERE id='22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222223';

UPDATE competencies SET description='Checking, reporting and taking immediate action during unsafe situations, participating in incident investigations, and supporting emergency response within the area.'
WHERE id='22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222224';

UPDATE competencies SET description='Front-line leadership covering: Safety Leadership (visible commitment to safety, LSR compliance, identifying and mitigating hazards); Team Leadership & People Management (developing and coaching subordinates); Decision Making & Problem Solving (timely decisions under pressure with appropriate escalation); and Planning, Work Coordination, and interface management.'
WHERE id='22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222230';

UPDATE competencies SET description='Emergency response covering: understanding of Major Accident Hazards (MAH); knowledge of ER Protocols (Tiers, Organisation, Roles & Responsibilities, Procedures); ER Leadership (taking command at site level, leading and delegating tasks effectively, responding to emergencies); communication and coordination with ER teams and other interfaces; and initiation of ER actions (e.g., activating FW system, PAGA, ESD hierarchy).'
WHERE id='22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222231';

UPDATE competencies SET description='Manage The Operation (MTO) capability covering: deep understanding of production system limitations, threats and opportunities; measurement and evaluation of production and equipment performance; proactive identification of threats and opportunities; simple RCAs (e.g., 5-Whys) to identify and resolve root causes; and effective use of MTO tools (e.g., dashboards).'
WHERE id='22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222232';

UPDATE competencies SET description='Permit to Work capability covering: understanding of the PTW process, procedures, and roles & responsibilities; review and authorisation of permits; and review and authorisation of process and equipment isolation.'
WHERE id='22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222233';

UPDATE competencies SET description='Understanding of the principles of Management of Change, identifying when and where an MoC is required, and initiating and implementing an MoC where applicable.'
WHERE id='22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222234';

UPDATE competencies SET description='Preparation of Daily Production and Critical Equipment Status Reports, Shift Handover Reports, and Shift Monitoring Plans.'
WHERE id='22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222235';

UPDATE competencies SET description='Understanding of Technical Integrity and the maintenance of Safety Critical Elements (SCE), and of Maintenance Work Processes and Tools (Work Preparation, Planning, and Execution).'
WHERE id='22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222236';
